Foxfingers flew low to the ground as he sped over the terrain on his
hoverboard. He was in Predacon territory once again only this time he didn't
hear fighting anywhere. he'd passed through once before and didn't have any
trouble maybe he'd go through it again. without any incidents. unfortunately
he knew that "maybe" was a big word.
